#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/catalog.ex:206
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Left click interact/walk, Right click examine/verb menu, Drag inventory "
"items to combine. F5 save/load, Ctrl+F5 options, Esc skip cutscene"
msgstr ""
"左鍵點擊交互/walk,右鍵點擊檢查/verb菜單,拖動目錄項目組合. F5 保存 /load, Ctrl+F5 選項, Esc 跳過切切換"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/catalog.ex:133
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "LibreQuake"
msgstr "自由夸克"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/librequake.ex:9
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"LibreQuake is a complete free and open-source replacement for Quake — "
"original levels, models, textures, sounds, and music all created by the "
"community under the BSD license. No commercial Quake files are needed."
msgstr ""
"LibreQuake是一個完全自由且開源的替換Quake——原始關卡,模型,紋理,聲音,以及音樂都是社區根據BSD許可證創建的. "
"不需要商業Quake文件 。"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/librequake.ex:17
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"LibreQuake runs on the same QuakeSpasm engine as the original, delivering "
"full 3D gameplay with mouselook, jumping, and all the movement mechanics "
"Quake is known for."
msgstr ""
"LibreQuake運行在與原作相同的QuakeSpasm引擎上,用鼠標外觀,跳躍來發送完整的3D遊戲玩法,所有運動力學Quake都以它聞名."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/librequake.ex:36
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"LibreQuake uses original community-made assets — the weapons and enemies "
"look different from Quake but play similarly."
msgstr "LibreQuake使用原有的社區制資產——武器和敵人看起來不同於Quake,但玩法類似."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/freedoom2.ex:13
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Like DOOM II, Phase 2 features larger, more complex levels with tougher "
"enemy encounters. The Super Shotgun (weapon slot 3, alternate) makes its "
"appearance here, and the level design takes full advantage of DOOM II's "
"expanded monster roster."
msgstr ""
"與DOOM II一樣,第2階段的特徵是更大,更復雜的關卡,敵人遭遇更激烈. Super "
"Shotgun(武器位置3,交替)在此出現,關卡設計充分利用了DOOM II擴展的怪物名冊."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/wolfenstein_3d.ex:38
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Listen for guards — you can hear enemies through doors before opening them."
msgstr "傾聽衛兵的呼聲——在打開門前,你可以聽到敵人的呼聲."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/catalog.ex:265
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Lure of the Temptress"
msgstr "誘惑者的光芒"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/scummvm_lure.ex:9
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Lure of the Temptress (1992) is Revolution Software's debut game — a "
"medieval fantasy adventure featuring the innovative Virtual Theatre engine. "
"The village of Turnvale has been conquered by the sorceress Selena and her "
"army of orcs known as Skorl."
msgstr ""
"Tempress的Lure (1992年)是革命軟件的首款遊戲——以創新的虛擬劇場引擎爲主角的中世紀幻想冒險. "
"特恩瓦勒村已被女巫塞琳娜及其被稱爲斯科爾的獸人軍隊征服."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/scummvm_bass.ex:17
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Made freeware by Revolution Software in 2003, Beneath a Steel Sky is widely "
"considered one of the greatest point-and-click adventures ever made. It runs"
" on ScummVM with full CD voice acting."
msgstr ""
"2003年由革命軟件製造自由軟件,在鋼鐵天空之下被廣泛認爲是有史以來最偉大的點擊冒險之一. 它在ScumVM上運行,並配有全CD的聲音演繹."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/scummvm_lure.ex:17
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Made freeware by Revolution Software, Lure of the Temptress is a piece of "
"adventure game history. While shorter and rougher than later Revolution "
"games (Beneath a Steel Sky, Broken Sword), its autonomous NPC system was "
"years ahead of its time."
msgstr ""
"革命軟件製造自由軟件 Tempress的Lure是冒險遊戲史上的一部作品. 雖然比後來的革命遊戲(Beneath a Steel Sky,Broken "
"Sword)更短,更粗糙,但其自主的NPC系統比時代早了數年."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/scummvm_fotaq.ex:17
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Made freeware by the developers, Flight of the Amazon Queen features full "
"voice acting on the CD version. It runs on ScummVM and is considered one of "
"the hidden gems of the 90s adventure game era."
msgstr "由開發者製作的自由軟件,亞馬遜皇后號的飛行在CD版本上具有全聲表演功能. 它運行於渣滓VM上,被認爲是90年代冒險遊戲時代的隱藏寶石之一."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/freedm.ex:37
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Maps are compact and weapon-dense — perfect for quick action sessions."
msgstr "地圖是緊湊和武器密集的——適合快速行動會議。"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/catalog.ex:266
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Medieval fantasy adventure (1992)"
msgstr "中世紀幻想冒險(1992)."

